ROCm Windows Installer v1.3
==========================

This MSI installer provides one-click installation of AMD ROCm on Windows 10/11 systems.

Features:
- Automated WSL2 setup with Ubuntu 22.04
- Complete ROCm 6.1.3 installation
- PyTorch 2.1.2 with ROCm support
- LM Studio GUI integration
- Hardware validation and compatibility checks

System Requirements:
- Windows 10 Pro/Enterprise/Education (Build 19041+) OR Windows 11
- AMD Radeon RX 7000 Series GPU or Ryzen AI APU
- 16GB+ RAM (32GB recommended)
- 50GB+ free disk space
- Administrator privileges

Installation:
1. Right-click this MSI file
2. Select "Run as Administrator"
3. Follow the installation wizard
4. Reboot if prompted

Note: This installer is signed with a self-signed certificate. Windows SmartScreen will show a warning - click "More info" then "Run anyway".

For documentation and support: https://github.com/OCNGill/Radeon_Open_Compute_ROCm_Installer_Windows_x64